<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="current-adj">current <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kʌrənt/    美 /'kɜːrənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[只用于名词前] 现在的；现今的；当前的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the current President
现任总统</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Students are placed into classes according to their current language skills.
根据学生当前的语言技能来分班。</p><footer>2016 天津</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>通用的；流通的；流行的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>current money
流通的货币</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a current account
活期存款账户</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>currently /'kʌrəntli/ adv   </p></div>